column5: We are heading up to the Whiteshell Provincial Park in southeastern Manitoba. Does any one know if there are any lake maps available for Falcon Lake or West Hawk Lake and where i could obtain them? Thanks in advance, Dave
If you don't mind printing your own:www.anglersatlas.comIt requires you to sign up, but it is free, and I haven't noticed any spam.
Thanks for all the great info,i really appreciate it.
